{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859273701,"sessionID":"ses_2868bbf9bffewN9nmTmbsFM6Qm","part":{"id":"prt_d797589a0001ZYHB05wc9ziqCO","messageID":"msg_d79757d7e001uihcp6Goi1BBug","sessionID":"ses_2868bbf9bffewN9nmTmbsFM6Qm","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_783999a0dae043ffa0c94d11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-019 — CLI Binary Entry Points (4 Binaries) Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Verify/Complete agentd (cmd/agentd/main.go)\n\n- [ ] **T001** Verify `cmd/agentd/main.go` - confirm it compiles and matches design:\n  - Uses controller-runtime manager\n  - Watches Sandbox CRD\n  - Imports `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd` reconciler\n  - Metrics disabled (`BindAddress: \"0\"`)\n  - Health probe disabled\n\n- [ ] **T002** Run `go build -o agentd ./cmd/agentd` to verify binary builds\n\n- [ ] **T003** Run `go vet ./cmd/agentd/...` to verify no vet errors\n\n### Phase 2: Complete picod (cmd/picod/main.go)\n\n- [ ] **T010** Update `cmd/picod/main.go` to add missing flags from design:\n  - `--auth-mode` (string, default: \"picod\")\n  - `--session-timeout` (duration, default: 15m)\n  - `--max-session-duration` (duration, default: 8h)\n\n- [ ] **T011** Update `pkg/picod/config.go` to include:\n  ```go\n  type Config struct {\n      Port              int\n      Workspace         string\n      AuthMode          string\n      SessionTimeout    time.Duration\n      MaxSessionDuration time.Duration\n  }\n  ```\n\n- [ ] **T012** Run `go build -o picod ./cmd/picod` to verify binary builds\n\n- [ ] **T013** Run `go vet ./cmd/picod/...` to verify no vet errors\n\n### Phase 3: Create workload-manager (cmd/workload-manager/main.go)\n\n- [ ] **T020** Create `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` with:\n  - Package main\n  - Import statements:\n    - `flag`\n    - `os`\n    - `time`\n    - `k8s.io/klog/v2`\n    - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n  - Command-line flags:\n    - `--listen-address` (string, default: \":8080\")\n    - `--kubeconfig` (string, default: \"\")\n    - `--shutdown-timeout` (duration, default: 30s)\n    - `--enable-metrics` (bool, default: false)\n    - `--enable-logging` (bool, default: true)\n  - Initialize K8s client: `workloadmanager.NewK8sClient(kubeconfig)`\n  - Create workload manager: `workloadmanager.NewWorkloadManager(k8sClient.Clientset)`\n  - Create server: `workloadmanager.NewServer(config, workloadMgr)`\n  - Start server: `server.Start()`\n\n- [ ] **T021** Run `go build -o workload-manager ./cmd/workload-manager` to verify binary builds\n\n- [ ] **T022** Run `go vet ./cmd/workload-manager/...` to verify no vet errors\n\n### Phase 4: Create router (cmd/router/main.go)\n\n- [ ] **T030** Create `cmd/router/main.go` with:\n  - Package main\n  - Import statements:\n    - `flag`\n    - `os`\n    - `time`\n    - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router`\n  - Command-line flags matching design:\n    - `--listen-address` (string, default: \":8080\")\n    - `--backend-timeout` (duration, default: 30s)\n    - `--idle-timeout` (duration, default: 60s)\n    - `--health-check-interval` (duration, default: 10s)\n    - `--health-check-timeout` (duration, default: 5s)\n    - `--max-conns-per-backend` (int, default: 100)\n    - `--rate-limit-enabled` (bool, default: false)\n    - `--rate-limit-rps` (int, default: 10)\n    - `--auth-enabled` (bool, default: false)\n    - `--auth-token` (string, default: \"\")\n    - `--session-enabled` (bool, default: false)\n    - `--session-timeout` (duration, default: 30m)\n    - `--session-cookie-name` (string, default: \"AGENTSESSIONID\")\n    - `--jwt-enabled` (bool, default: false)\n    - `--jwt-secret` (string, default: \"\")\n    - `--jwt-algorithm` (string, default: \"HS256\")\n    - `--jwt-private-key-path` (string, default: \"\")\n    - `--jwt-public-key-path` (string, default: \"\")\n  - Create router config from flags\n  - Start router: `router.RunWithSignal(config)`\n\n- [ ] **T031** Add initial backend configuration (workload-manager URL):\n  - Add `--workload-manager-url` flag to cmd/router/main.go\n  - Add backend to router pool on startup\n\n- [ ] **T032** Run `go build -o router ./cmd/router` to verify binary builds\n\n- [ ] **T033** Run `go vet ./cmd/router/...` to verify no vet errors\n\n### Phase 5: Integration & Build Verification\n\n- [ ] **T040** Run `go mod tidy` - ensure dependencies resolved\n\n- [ ] **T041** Run `go build ./cmd/...` - verify all 4 binaries build\n\n- [ ] **T042** Run `go vet ./cmd/...` - verify no vet errors in any binary\n\n- [ ] **T043** Verify binary structure matches design.md:\n  ```\n  cmd/\n  ├── agentd/main.go\n  ├── picod/main.go\n  ├── router/main.go\n  └── workload-manager/main.go\n  ```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- **T001**: None (existing code review)\n- **T002**: T001\n- **T003**: T002\n- **T010**: None (existing code update)\n- **T011**: T010\n- **T012**: T011\n- **T013**: T012\n- **T020**: None (new file creation)\n- **T021**: T020\n- **T022**: T021\n- **T030**: None (new file creation)\n- **T031**: T030\n- **T032**: T031\n- **T033**: T032\n- **T040**: All implementation tasks (T001-T033)\n- **T041**: T040\n- **T042**: T041\n- **T043**: T041\n\n---\n\n## Configuration Variables\n\n### agentd\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| KUBECONFIG | No | in-cluster | Kubernetes config path |\n\n### picod\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| KUBECONFIG | No | in-cluster | Kubernetes config path |\n\n### workload-manager\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| --listen-address | No | :8080 | HTTP server listen address |\n| --kubeconfig | No | in-cluster | Kubernetes config path |\n| --shutdown-timeout | No | 30s | Graceful shutdown timeout |\n\n### router\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| --listen-address | No | :8080 | HTTP server listen address |\n| --workload-manager-url | Yes | - | WorkloadManager backend URL |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Notes\n\n### Binary Entry Points\n\n| Binary | Entry Point | Purpose |\n|--------|-------------|---------|\n| agentd | cmd/agentd/main.go | Kubernetes controller for AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRDs |\n| picod | cmd/picod/main.go | Code execution daemon inside sandbox pods |\n| router | cmd/router/main.go | HTTP session router with auth/session management |\n| workload-manager | cmd/workload-manager/main.go | REST API for sandbox lifecycle management |\n\n### Key Behaviors\n\n1. **agentd**: Runs as K8s controller using controller-runtime, watches Sandbox resources\n2. **picod**: HTTP server for code execution inside sandbox pods\n3. **router**: Proxies requests to workload-manager, handles session affinity\n4. **workload-manager**: REST API that creates/manages AgentRuntime CRs\n\n### Package Dependencies\n\n- `cmd/agentd` → `pkg/agentd`\n- `cmd/picod` → `pkg/picod`\n- `cmd/router` → `pkg/router`, `pkg/store`\n- `cmd/workload-manager` → `pkg/workloadmanager`, `pkg/client`\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design Doc: `design.md` (AR-019)\n- Module: `cmd`\n- Related: `pkg/agentd`, `pkg/picod`, `pkg/router`, `pkg/workloadmanager`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/cmd/picod/main.go\">\nERROR [24:39] not enough arguments in call to picod.NewServer\n\thave (*picod.Config)\n\twant (*picod.Config, *picod.AuthConfig)\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark